  <div>
    <div class="flex gap-3 mb-2 items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex gap-3 items-center">
            <h1 class="text-lg sm:text-2xl font-semibold mt-0 mb-4">
              Anomalies • unusual install changes
            </h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <nav class="tabs">
      <a data-match="exact" href="/">Listings</a>
      <a data-match="include" href="/categories/">Categories</a>
      <a data-match="exact" href="/top-ranking/">Top ranking</a>
      <a data-match="exact" href="/installs/">Installs</a>
      <a data-match="include" href="/anomalies/">Anomalies</a>
      <a data-match="include" href="/apps/archive/">Archive</a>
    </nav>

    <p>Apps whose weekly install rate doubled or halved, comparing installs gained in the last
    7 days against installs gained in the 7 days before that.</p>
    <p>This is about the rate of change, not the total
    install count, so it catches a large app suddenly accelerating (or stalling back out) just as well as a
    small app doubling in size.</p>
    <p>Only changes where the larger side of the comparison is at least
    {{ 100 | numberFormat }} installs are shown, to keep tiny apps from flooding the list with meaningless swings.</p>

    <p class="text-sm">This data is refreshed daily sometime between 00:00 and 03:00 UTC, alongside the
    <a href="/installs/">install history</a>.</p>

    {% if pagination.pageNumber == 0 %}
      {% if anomalies.latest.length > 0 %}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg md:text-2xl mt-6 font-semibold">New today ({{ anomalies.latestBuildDate | formatDate }})</h2>
          <p class="text-xs">Anomalies first detected in today's build.</p>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 mt-2">
            {% for episode in anomalies.latest %}
              {% include "partials/anomaly-item.njk" %}
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <hr class="my-8">
      {% else %}
        <p class="text-xs italic">No new anomalies detected in today's build.</p>
      {% endif %}
    {% endif %}

    <div class="chart-container">
      <h2 class="text-lg md:text-2xl mt-0 font-semibold">All anomalies</h2>
      <p class="text-xs">Every detected jump or drop since we started collecting data, most recent first.</p>

      {% if episodes.length > 0 %}
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 mt-2">
          {% for episode in episodes %}
            {% include "partials/anomaly-item.njk" %}
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      {% else %}
        <p class="text-xs italic">No anomalies found.</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    {% if pagination.pages.length > 1 %}
      <nav class="flex items-center justify-between mt-8 text-sm">
        <div>
          {% if pagination.href.previous %}
            <a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}" class="badge">&larr; Newer</a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-600">
          Page {{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }} of {{ pagination.pages.length }}
        </div>
        <div>
          {% if pagination.href.next %}
            <a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}" class="badge">Older &rarr;</a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </nav>
    {% endif %}

  </div>
